{
  "description": "A nighttime panoramic view captures a vibrant cityscape illuminated with lights and a spectacular fireworks display. In the foreground, a long, modern bridge stretches across dark water, its lights reflecting on the surface. The bridge's structure is sleek and minimalist, featuring multiple supports and a cable-stayed design. Beyond the bridge, the city skyline is densely packed with buildings of varying heights, most of which are adorned with twinkling lights. A grand, illuminated archway is prominent in the middle ground. Above the cityscape, a burst of colorful fireworks explodes in the sky, creating a dazzling spectacle. The fireworks display consists of shades of red, blue, and gold. The overall scene evokes a sense of celebration and wonder.",
